Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't do it." "It's too frustrating."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break down those hurdles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is being manipulated on the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not frightened yet I get told to go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The path to the unseen future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not be able to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes, and shuffle your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, yes! you are the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never lose! Shuffle your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Fiery Dance Battle"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure wish it'd stop raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Jounouchi, what's up with Shizuka-chan's operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Thanks to Yugi, I was able to hire the world's most elite doctor to come heal her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation's gonna be soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll be there when it happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, thanks to my dad and mom getting divorced, we've lives separate from each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell're ya talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}gotta{\i0} go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell're {\i1}you{\i0} coming along?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-chan looks completely different than you! She's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta introduce us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So {\i1}that's{\i0} what you were after?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... free this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, my other self hasn't been himself recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't talk to me much either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought... he'd feel better if he saw you, Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The other Yugi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Well, I gotta help Grandpa out at the store!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet at Domino Station Sunday at 10:00 A.M.!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... That all happened so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This stands out too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? You're suddenly getting nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I promised to meet with Anzu today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}date{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About {\i1}time{\i0} you worked up the guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's a date, it's not gonna be with {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A date... with the other Yugi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was pretty sure the other Yugi was just another personality that came out through the Millennium Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What am I getting so nervous for? Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to you, my other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-hey! What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're just sitting here saying nothing... This is so awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go check this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ancient Egypt exhibit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-See? This mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as your Millennium Puzzle, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that puzzle may have some connection to Egypt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's just that he...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he put these on in front of the mirror this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize it was because of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hides his real self in order to fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's worried about {\i1}you{\i0}, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got no need to worry about {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even know what is is he wants {\i1}himself{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I am now, he's looking for who he really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who he really is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did I come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how to find this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like I thought, the Yugi in front of me is an entirely different personality than the usual Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So he's been living within the Millennium Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine the way I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I myself don't know exactly who I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, I told you that I dream of becoming a dancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that I want to head to America after graduating school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, that dream is getting closer and closer to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's running out, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll realize your dream, Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know myself it won't be an easy dream to obtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if there's even the slightest chance of me realizing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna believe in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go walk the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you will find out who you are! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going, Anzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter {\i1}where{\i0} we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(317,325)}"Duel Monsters"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know there was a card shop here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just opened recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Duel Monsters Booster Packs"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't decide what to buy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the happiest he's been all day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This is sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightforce Sword, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a good card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My partner's gonna be thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go there next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! That's the stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! He wiped the floor with 'im!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's cuz Step Johnny's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who wants to challenge me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance Battle Game, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey~! Sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna battle me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to face him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run from a challenge to dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even {\i1}you{\i0} can stop me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure got some guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweetheart, you're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose to Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's just have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't {\i1}need{\i0} you to hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, come hang out with me tonight if I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you were {\i1}really{\i0} after, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Music! Standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's {\i1}amazing{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! She's matching his steps perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really a good match for Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's low, Step Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one, sweety!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not bad, Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A {\b0}miss{\b1}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone as great as {\b0}me{\b1}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chick's freakin' amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johnny's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She owned Step Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe spending 100 yen on a game could renew my dream this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can maintain that dream even if I don't go after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really think that's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know more about myself... Where I came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I keep things the way they are, I'll always be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must want it this way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other Yugi has already discovered his other self...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish the other Yugi will always be here, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you have two hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must take control of your own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So be true to yourself and your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gettin' away like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's have a {\i1}Duel{\i0} this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A{\i1} Duel{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose the Duel, I'll give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else, you'll be my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just wanna show off in front of her, that it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you leave this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! She's mine anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if {\i1}I{\i0} win, you'll never show up\Nin front of Anzu ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, {\i1}if{\i0} you can beat me and my Street Duel Strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't it obvious? To be popular, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to pick up nice chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's bet her dreams on dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let you defile Anzu's dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such stupid shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be a true dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound Maiden, in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use this to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf's Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle! Use your "Elf's Slash" move to destroy the Sound Maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using a sword on woman...\N That's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's {\i1}my{\i0} turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My cute Water Dancer baby, in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the? It's just a Fan Deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fan Deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A deck not really used to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are cards that evolve from\Nthe player's own interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His cards are all about dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you underestimate them,\Nyou got it coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show a Duel I put my entire {\i1}soul{\i0} into.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then show me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This "soul" you speak of!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn without doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits of the Harp in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the Magic Card,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chorus Sanctuary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card's Attack effect
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of any Monster in Defense Mode by 500 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was hopeless
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I saw his honesty\Nin the way he plays.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But a Duel is a Duel!\N Let's finish this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step Johnny! Your showtime's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse of Dragon! Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell Flame!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I forgot to use Defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dumb {\i1}is{\i0} this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that "soul" of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet!\N My stage is only getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witch of the Black Forest in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? He's not using a Fan Deck anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To fuse Witch of the Black Forest with High Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Musician King!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle! I attack the Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf's Swordsman was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Musician King puts his whole {\i1}soul{\i0} into that guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I can start looking forward to my night with the babe over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card on the field and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can do it, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Curse of Dragon to attack the Musician King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Metal Conversion - Magic Reflection Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card transforms Musician King into Heavy Metal King and powers it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna play a nice tune for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you got no Monsters left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he really this strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giant Soldier of Stone in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed so arrogant, but ain't ya weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Metal Conversion doesn't just increase his Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Heavy Metal King!\N Attack and destroy the Giant Soldier of Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant solider too...Giant Soldier of Stone as well...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It adds half the attacked Monster's Attack Points to the equipped Monster's Attack Strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Black Magician in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician, attack the Heavy Metal King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Have you forgotten?\N I've got Metal Conversion's Effect here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician is doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... misinterpreting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Metal Conversion's Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,''Heavy Metal King'' is defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why didn't Metal Conversion's Effect activate!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Monster equipped with this card attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,half of the opponent's Attack Points\Nwill be added to its own Attack Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Heavy Metal King attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician's Attack Power is halved and added to your Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Effect doesn't activate when {\i1}I'm{\i0} the one attacking,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and so it keeps its original 2500 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were too {\i1}careless{\i0}, Step Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?! What's your name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that name from somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who beat Pegasus in the Duelist Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0} Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try and beat me in this game, though I don't plan on losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I quit! I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I defeat\Nthe Duelist Kingdom winner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the time to pick up "chicks",
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why not spend more time\Non what you do best?! Like dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should bet everything on my dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're better at dancing\Nthan you are at Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I'm good at better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a pro dancer\Nis a faraway dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been to any auditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave up after {\i1}one{\i0} try?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how it feels to be a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've failed more than a {\i1}dozen{\i0} times!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because running away\Ndoes not solve the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pace yourself and the future will open up to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... you also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sounded a bit arrogant back there, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the Ancient Egyptian exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are clues about my past here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must go in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel like my heart's resisting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'm afraid to learn the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But today...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made the decision to do this after meeting with you, Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I? Where am I from?\NThe answers are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Lift your head up high!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(133,153)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to the museum\Nto find a clue about his lost memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw a 3000-year-old\Nstone tablet there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On it is an image or a Pharaoh\Nthat looks {\i1}exactly{\i0} like Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other Yugi is sure that\Nhe is the soul of that pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is this "battle to regain my memories" about that's starting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time! "This Town Becomes Battle City"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.38,0:22:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've been here, been in this place before
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.81,0:22:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the classroom shaded by the setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I laughed along and pointed with my too shortly cut bangs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little, time keeps going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:23:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bangs now over my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sunset took everyone together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure nothing changed while we were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.27,0:23:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.44,0:23:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept on searching for something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.61,0:23:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you understood such a senseless time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here, always...
